  ('3a7923aa-a288-4d5d-9fc5-a4d95b69cc65', '19 on the Greenway', '3619-3681 Arbutus St', 'Vancouver', 'BC', 49.2541526, -123.1534333, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/3a7923aa-a288-4d5d-9fc5-a4d95b69cc65.jpg?t=1776639981869', 2025, 118, 'PCI Developments', 'PBR', NULL, 'https://19onthegreenway.com/floorplans', '{"scroll": true, "strategy": "playwright_render", "scroll_count": 10, "additional_urls": ["https://19onthegreenway.com/"], "extraction_hint": "This site shows (1) building-level ''starting from'' rents by bed type near the top (e.g. ''1 Bedrooms from $2,750'', ''2 Bedrooms from $3,750''; Studios and 3 Bedrooms may say ''Fully Leased'') and (2) a grid of floor plan cards further down. Each card has a unit-type code (e.g. A3, A5, A7, C3, C5), square footage, bed count, bath count, and an optional ''FINAL UNIT'' badge. Cards do NOT show per-card rents. Emit one unit_data row per visible card, using the card''s sqft/bed/bath and applying the matching ''starting from'' rent as rent_price. If a bed type is ''Fully Leased'', do not emit rows for it. Preserve the card''s letter code (e.g. ''A3'') in raw_text/notes. Capture the ''$500 Signing Bonus + Up to 2 Months Free Rent'' banner (on the homepage) as building-level incentive/promo text, not as a unit.", "initial_wait_ms": 6000}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-03-20T03:32:43.237415+00:00'),
