  ('6c5193e1-721a-4ed1-9cba-46d04143340b', 'Livmore', '55 Gerrard Street East', 'Toronto', 'ON', 43.6592, -79.3786, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/6c5193e1-721a-4ed1-9cba-46d04143340b.jpg?t=1771464022366', 2018, 594, 'GWL', 'PBR', 'https://www.gwlraresidential.com/apartments/on/toronto/the-livmore-bay-gerrard/', 'https://www.gwlraresidential.com/apartments/on/toronto/the-livmore-bay-gerrard/floorplans', '{"notes": "GWL/RentCafe/Yardi site. Main page has plan-level sqft in data attributes (injected via pre_capture_js). Subpages have individual unit rents. Cookie popup auto-dismissed.", "scroll": true, "strategy": "playwright_render", "scroll_count": 3, "pre_capture_js": "document.querySelectorAll(''[data-floorplan-name]'').forEach(el => { const name = el.getAttribute(''data-floorplan-name''); const sqft = el.getAttribute(''data-floorplan-sqft''); const price = el.getAttribute(''data-floorplan-price''); if (name && sqft) { const div = document.createElement(''div''); div.textContent = ''[PLAN DATA] '' + name + '' | Sqft: '' + sqft + '' | Price: '' + price; div.style.fontSize = ''14px''; el.parentElement.insertBefore(div, el); } }); document.querySelectorAll(''.fp-container img[src]'').forEach(img => { const src = decodeURIComponent(img.src.split(''/'').pop()); const match = src.match(/(\\d+)sf/i); const nameMatch = src.match(/lbg%20(.+?)%20\\d/); if (match) { const div = document.createElement(''div''); div.textContent = ''[PLAN IMAGE] '' + src.replace(/.jpg$/i, '''').replace(/%20/g, '' ''); div.style.fontSize = ''12px''; img.parentElement.insertBefore(div, img); } });", "additional_urls": ["https://www.gwlraresidential.com/apartments/on/toronto/the-livmore-bay-gerrard/floorplans/studio", "https://www.gwlraresidential.com/apartments/on/toronto/the-livmore-bay-gerrard/floorplans/1-bedroom-1-bath", "https://www.gwlraresidential.com/apartments/on/toronto/the-livmore-bay-gerrard/floorplans/2-bedroom-2-bath"], "initial_wait_ms": 8000}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-02-18T13:56:30.68652+00:00'),
  ('6d2a3b2c-5b67-4b5a-81f8-af45d62f87f1', 'Revolve', '3572 Glen Dr', 'Vancouver', 'BC', 49.2531308, -123.0813783, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/6d2a3b2c-5b67-4b5a-81f8-af45d62f87f1.jpg?t=1776642156146', 2025, 100, 'Peterson Group', 'PBR', NULL, 'https://revolve.petersonrentals.com/floorplans', '{"scroll": true, "strategy": "akamai_stealth", "scroll_count": 6, "extraction_hint": "This is a Peterson Rentals / Revolve Vancouver site. It has a main /floorplans page with plan CARDS, plus per-plan subpages appended after markers like \"<!-- SUBPAGE: https://revolve.petersonrentals.com/floorplans/... -->\".\n\nMAIN PAGE:\n- Each floor plan card shows: plan name (e.g., \"STUDIO - G\", \"1 BDR - Z\", \"2 BDR - AE\"), bed count, bath count, sqft (e.g., \"602 Sq. Ft.\"), and either \"Starting at $X /Month\" + \"Availability\" OR \"Call for details\" + \"Contact Us\".\n- IGNORE any plan whose card says \"Call for details\" / \"Contact Us\" — those plans have zero available units. Do not emit rows for them.\n\nSUBPAGES (after \"SUBPAGE:\" markers):\n- Each subpage represents ONE floor plan. It contains an \"Available Units\" section listing individual apartments:\n  \"Apartment: # 0205\"\n  \"Starting at: $2,068/Month\"\n- A plan may have multiple apartments listed. Each \"Apartment: # XXXX\" line + its nearest \"Starting at: $X,XXX/Month\" line = ONE unit row.\n- The subpage also states the sqft near top (\"Up to 602 Sq. Ft.\" or similar) — use that for every unit on that subpage.\n- The plan header on the subpage (e.g., \"STUDIO - G (Below Market Housing - Conditions Apply)\") + \"Studio | 1 Bathroom\" indicates unit_type + bathrooms.\n\nEXTRACTION RULES:\n1. EMIT ONE ROW PER \"Apartment: # XXXX\" LISTING in the subpage \"Available Units\" sections.\n2. For each unit:\n   - unit_type: from the subpage plan header (\"Studio\" → \"bachelor\", \"1 Bedroom\" → \"1-bed\", \"2 Bedroom\" → \"2-bed\", etc.)\n   - bathrooms: \"1\", \"2\", etc. from the \"| N Bathroom\" line\n   - square_footage: the integer from \"Up to N Sq. Ft.\" on the subpage (e.g., 602). If not present, fall back to the main page card sqft for the same plan.\n   - rent_price: the number from \"Starting at: $X,XXX/Month\" stripping $ and commas (e.g., \"$2,068\" → 2068)\n   - rent_psf: rent_price / square_footage\n   - notes: plan name + unit number (e.g., \"Plan STUDIO - G, Unit #0205\")\n   - raw_text: short like \"STUDIO - G #0205 — 602 sqft — $2,068/Month\"\n3. Do NOT emit rows from the main /floorplans cards — subpages are authoritative.\n4. If a subpage is missing or returned zero apartment listings, emit nothing for that plan.\n5. Ignore Cloudflare \"Just a moment...\" placeholder pages, recaptcha/form fields, leasing office address, and footer text.\n\nAlso extract any building-wide incentives (e.g., \"Below Market Housing\", \"Limited Time Offer\", \"1 Month Free\"). The footer note \"*On Select Homes for a Limited Time. Conditions Apply.\" is a generic disclaimer, not an incentive.", "initial_wait_ms": 10000, "dynamic_subpage_wait_ms": 7000, "dynamic_additional_urls_selector": "a.track-apply"}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-03-20T03:32:43.237415+00:00'),
  ('6d5005e1-eb82-42e5-b4b7-63a1a9509fb0', 'Limelight Condos', '360 Square One Dr', 'Mississauga', 'ON', 43.5974007, -79.6409826, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/6d5005e1-eb82-42e5-b4b7-63a1a9509fb0.jpg?t=1776641740957', 2010, 400, NULL, 'Condo', NULL, 'https://condos.ca/mississauga/limelight-north-tower-360-square-one-dr-370-square-one-dr', '{"scroll": true, "strategy": "playwright_render", "scroll_count": 10, "pre_capture_js": "(async function() { var elems = document.querySelectorAll(''a, button, span, div''); for (var i = 0; i < elems.length; i++) { if (elems[i].textContent.trim().match(/^Show All/)) { elems[i].click(); await new Promise(function(r) { setTimeout(r, 1500); }); } } window.scrollTo(0, document.body.scrollHeight); await new Promise(function(r) { setTimeout(r, 2000); }); })()", "initial_wait_ms": 8000}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-03-20T03:33:06.247444+00:00'),
  ('73cefc53-fe11-499d-a2e5-4858c5f77d3c', 'Story of Midtown', '75 Broadway Ave', 'Toronto', 'ON', 43.7099581, -79.3945147, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/73cefc53-fe11-499d-a2e5-4858c5f77d3c.jpg?t=1771351045229', 2025, 336, 'Hazelview', 'PBR', NULL, 'https://www.mystorymidtown.com/suites', '{"scroll": true, "strategy": "playwright_render", "scroll_count": 6, "pre_capture_js": "(async function() { function delay(ms) { return new Promise(function(r) { setTimeout(r, ms); }); } function click(el) { el.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent(''click'', {bubbles: true, cancelable: true})); } function walkText(root) { var walker = document.createTreeWalker(root, NodeFilter.SHOW_TEXT); var text = ''''; var node; while (node = walker.nextNode()) { var p = node.parentElement; if (p && (p.tagName === ''STYLE'' || p.tagName === ''SCRIPT'')) continue; var t = node.textContent.trim(); if (t.length > 1) text += t + '' ''; } return text.replace(/\\s+/g, '' '').trim(); } var fpn = null, sr = null, floors = null; for (var i = 0; i < 30; i++) { fpn = document.querySelector(''floorplan-navigator.fpn-one''); if (fpn && fpn.shadowRoot) { sr = fpn.shadowRoot; floors = sr.querySelectorAll(''li.unit-filters__floor''); if (floors.length) break; } await delay(500); } if (!fpn || !sr || !floors || !floors.length) { var errDiv = document.createElement(''div''); errDiv.id = ''fpn-extracted''; errDiv.textContent = ''[FPN-73-BROADWAY ERROR: not rendered after 15s]''; document.body.appendChild(errDiv); return; } var pieces = [''[FPN-73-BROADWAY floors='' + floors.length + '']'']; for (var j = 0; j < floors.length; j++) { click(floors[j]); await delay(450); pieces.push(walkText(sr)); } var div = document.createElement(''div''); div.id = ''fpn-extracted''; div.textContent = pieces.join(''\\n---FLOOR---\\n''); document.body.appendChild(div); })();", "extraction_hint": "This page lists units for 73 Broadway only (Story of Midtown). The pre_capture_js dumps each floor''s units between ''---FLOOR---'' separators. Each unit appears as ''Unit XXXX'' followed by bedroom count (e.g. ''3 Bedrooms'', ''2 Bathroom''), interior sqft (e.g. ''935 SqFt''), price (e.g. ''$4,280''), and availability. The same unit may appear in multiple floor sections — extract each unique ''Unit XXXX'' once. Ignore any 75 Broadway content (should not be present). Building name: ''Story of Midtown''.", "initial_wait_ms": 8000, "section_wait_ms": 3000}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-02-13T19:12:54.105789+00:00'),
  ('756235bb-f995-47b1-9cdb-9be6fc8e9280', 'LIV Montreal', '1380 Boulevard René-Lévesque Ouest', 'Montreal', 'QC', 45.4955392, -73.5730301, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/756235bb-f995-47b1-9cdb-9be6fc8e9280.jpg?t=1771955497958', 2018, 239, 'Summit PM', 'PBR', NULL, 'https://www.summitmanagement.ca/apartments/liv', '{"scroll": true, "strategy": "playwright_render", "scroll_count": 3, "initial_wait_ms": 5000}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-02-22T23:28:04.833678+00:00'),
  ('76e56464-b375-4840-bb79-6b5de3354321', 'Marlow (Block D)', '980 Dufferin St', 'Toronto', 'ON', 43.6588048, -79.4354243, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/76e56464-b375-4840-bb79-6b5de3354321.jpg?t=1771970490503', 2026, 214, 'Fitzrovia', 'PBR', NULL, NULL, '{}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-02-24T18:17:19.63003+00:00'),
  ('788c5a9c-9951-411b-8824-2ff21ce0b24b', 'Signal', '8428 Ash St', 'Vancouver', 'BC', 49.2591203, -123.1176755, 'https://yckzayjlcvxinxcebyuf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/comp-building-photos/788c5a9c-9951-411b-8824-2ff21ce0b24b.jpg?t=1776642239232', 2025, 524, 'Intracorp', 'PBR', NULL, 'https://www.rentsignal.ca/suites', '{"scroll": true, "strategy": "playwright_render", "scroll_count": 6, "pre_capture_js": "\n(async function() {\n  const host = document.querySelector(''floorplan-navigator'');\n  if (!host || !host.shadowRoot) return;\n  const sr = host.shadowRoot;\n  const floors = sr.querySelectorAll(''li.unit-filters__floor'');\n  if (!floors.length) return;\n  const allLines = [''=== SIGNAL PER-UNIT LISTINGS (RentSync FPN shadow DOM) ===''];\n  let totalUnits = 0;\n  for (let i = 0; i < floors.length; i++) {\n    floors[i].dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent(''click'', {bubbles: true, cancelable: true}));\n    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1200));\n    const cards = sr.querySelectorAll(''.unit-listing__item'');\n    const floorLabel = (floors[i].textContent || '''').trim().replace(/\\s+/g, '' '');\n    const floorLines = ['''', ''FLOOR: '' + floorLabel + '' ('' + cards.length + '' suites)''];\n    const seen = new Set();\n    for (const c of cards) {\n      const inner = c.querySelector(''.unit-card'') || c;\n      const id = inner.getAttribute(''data-unit-id'') || (inner.outerHTML.length + '':'' + inner.textContent.slice(0, 30));\n      if (seen.has(id)) continue;\n      seen.add(id);\n      const num = (c.querySelector(''.unit-card__title--number'') ? c.querySelector(''.unit-card__title--number'').textContent.trim() : '''').replace(/\\s+/g, '' '');\n      const bed = (c.querySelector(''.unit-card__bed'') ? c.querySelector(''.unit-card__bed'').textContent.trim() : '''').replace(/\\s+/g, '' '');\n      const bath = (c.querySelector(''.unit-card__bath'') ? c.querySelector(''.unit-card__bath'').textContent.trim() : '''').replace(/\\s+/g, '' '');\n      const sqft = (c.querySelector(''.unit-card__sqFt'') ? c.querySelector(''.unit-card__sqFt'').textContent.trim() : '''').replace(/\\s+/g, '' '');\n      floorLines.push(''  '' + num + '' | '' + bed + '' | '' + bath + '' | '' + sqft);\n      totalUnits++;\n    }\n    if (floorLines.length > 2) allLines.push(...floorLines);\n  }\n  allLines.push('''');\n  allLines.push(''TOTAL UNITS EXTRACTED FROM FPN: '' + totalUnits);\n  const pre = document.createElement(''pre'');\n  pre.id = ''signal-units-dump'';\n  pre.style.cssText = ''display:block;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:monospace;padding:20px;z-index:1;position:relative;'';\n  pre.textContent = allLines.join(''\\n'');\n  document.body.appendChild(pre);\n})();\n", "extraction_hint": "This is the Signal (Vancouver) /suites page. The building uses a RentSync \"floorplan-navigator\" web component whose shadow DOM has been flattened into a plain-text dump starting with \"=== SIGNAL PER-UNIT LISTINGS ===\". The dump contains one line per available unit in the format:\n  <unit #> | <beds> | <baths> | <sqft>\ngrouped under \"FLOOR: <N>\" headers.\n\nExample dump lines:\n  Unit 1 | 3 Bedrooms + Den | 2 Bathroom | 1429 SqFt\n  Unit 101 | 2 Bedrooms | 2 Bathroom | 726 SqFt\n  Unit 102 | 1 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom | 656 SqFt\n\nSEPARATELY, the [PROMOTIONAL CONTEXT] block at the top of the content contains building-wide \"Starting From Pricing\" by unit type, e.g.:\n  Studio: $1995 | 1Bed: $2160 | 2Bed: $2755 | 3Bed: $3900 | Townhome: $3735\n(Exact dollar values change week to week — always re-read from the promo context.)\n\nEXTRACTION RULES:\n1. EMIT ONE ROW PER UNIT LINE in the \"=== SIGNAL PER-UNIT LISTINGS ===\" dump.\n2. For each unit line:\n   - unit_type: from the bed count (\"Studio\" → \"bachelor\", \"1 Bedroom\" → \"1-bed\", \"1 Bedroom + Den\" → \"1-bed+den\", \"2 Bedrooms\" → \"2-bed\", \"2 Bedrooms + Den\" → \"2-bed+den\", \"3 Bedrooms\" → \"3-bed\", \"3 Bedrooms + Den\" → \"3-bed+den\")\n   - bathrooms: \"1\", \"2\", \"1.5\", etc. (strip \"Bathroom\"/\"Bathrooms\")\n   - square_footage: integer from \"NNN SqFt\" (e.g., 1429)\n   - rent_price: the matching \"Starting From\" rent from the promotional context\n     - \"bachelor\" → Studio price (e.g., 1995)\n     - \"1-bed\" or \"1-bed+den\" → 1Bed price (e.g., 2160)\n     - \"2-bed\" or \"2-bed+den\" → 2Bed price (e.g., 2755)\n     - \"3-bed\" or \"3-bed+den\" → 3Bed price (e.g., 3900)\n     - Townhome → map to its bed count; use Townhome price ($3735) if a townhome label appears\n   - rent_psf: rent_price / square_footage (e.g., 1995/440 = 4.53)\n   - notes: plan name / floor / unit number (e.g., \"Floor 1, Unit 101\")\n   - raw_text: short like \"Unit 101 — Floor 1 — 726 SqFt — $2,755\"\n3. Do NOT emit rows from the promotional \"Starting From\" list directly — that list is ONLY used to populate rent_price on the per-unit rows.\n4. If a unit has no sqft (rare), still emit the row with square_footage=null.\n5. Ignore cookie banners, book-a-tour forms, leasing office info, and footer legal text.\n\nAlso capture current building-wide incentives (e.g., \"Sign a 12-month lease and get a MacBook Neo*\", \"1 Month Free\", or similar). The MacBook offer is valid March 20 - August 31, 2026.", "initial_wait_ms": 10000}'::jsonb, TRUE, '2026-03-20T03:32:43.237415+00:00'),
